---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SiteHeader from "../../components/SiteHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="For Teachers — ChristmasTreeTurner.com"
	description="Every bounty we pay honors four decades in the classroom. Help solve a family mystery, and teachers win."
>
	<SiteHeader />

	<main id="main-content" class="mt-24">
		<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			<a href="/" class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted hover:text-text transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to Home</a>

			<h1 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-4xl md:text-6xl italic mb-4 text-red" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">For Teachers</h1>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">A Family Hunt Honoring Four Decades in the Classroom</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">My mom taught for over 40 years. She believed in curiosity, persistence, and helping people discover answers. This hunt to trace our family's vintage Christmas Tree Turner is exactly the kind of mystery she'd love&mdash;and every bounty we pay honors her legacy by supporting teachers and schools.</p>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">How This Benefits Educators</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Every verified lead that moves us closer to the origin earns a donation to a teacher or school of the finder's choosing. That means:</p>

			<ul class="pl-5 list-disc grid gap-2 mb-6 text-lg">
				<li>You could be the researcher who solves it</li>
				<li>Or a colleague might nominate you as the recipient</li>
				<li>Either way, teachers win</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">How You Can Help</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold">Share with the right people:</span></p>

			<ul class="pl-5 list-disc grid gap-2 mb-6 text-lg">
				<li>History buffs, antique collectors, librarians</li>
				<li>Local historians or museum curators</li>
				<li>Alumni networks with long memories</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold">Use it as a teaching moment:</span></p>

			<ul class="pl-5 list-disc grid gap-2 mb-6 text-lg">
				<li>Older students can practice archival research</li>
				<li>It's real detective work with real stakes</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold">Connect us:</span></p>

			<ul class="pl-5 list-disc grid gap-2 mb-6 text-lg">
				<li>Know someone who might know someone? Introductions matter.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mt-12 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">Spread the Word</h2>

			<p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Sometimes the best contribution is just telling the right person this hunt exists. Questions or leads? <a href="mailto:clark@superfun.team" class="text-accent hover:underline">clark@superfun.team</a></p>

			<div class="bg-accent text-white p-8 mt-12">
				<h2 class="uppercase tracking-tight text-2xl italic mb-3" style="font-family: 'Tay Highbeams', sans-serif;">Ready to Help?</h2>
				<p class="text-white/80 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">Send us what you find — or just say hello.</p>
				<a href="/#contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-white text-accent font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">Submit a Lead</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<footer class="border-t border-border pt-16 mt-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			<p class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted">
				This is a personal historical research project. No commercial use intended.
			</p>
			<p class="font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mt-2">
				Help, questions, and press inquiries: clark@superfun.team
			</p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
